name: treasure
description:
life is never predictable right? we sometimes get a treasure from things we do not expect. like sometimes things that we think are not important are things that we will be grateful for in the future. like this NFT world, I never thought I would jump in it and this has become a valuable experience for me now. I made many friends and also a place to express myself.

therefore, love your destiny as much as possible. be grateful for your life.
